extends email-layout

block content
    h2 Password Reset
    p Hi. You have requested a password reset. Please click the following button to continue on with resetting your password. Please note this link is only valide for the next hour.
    +button(resetURL, 'Reset my Password')
    P If you can't click the above button please visit #{resetURL}
    br
    p If you didn't request this email, please ignore it.